  "Description": {
    "English": "A powerful upgrade for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Exosuit Jetpack</span>, allowing limited <span class=\"name name-stellar\">jetpack recharging</span> while airborne.<br><br>Highly efficient compressors fitted around the jetpack exhaust take advantage of the windflow generated by <span class=\"name name-stellar\">persistent falling</span>, recycling some of that energy into jetpack fuel.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "用于<span class=\"name name-technology\">套装喷气背包</span>的强大升级组件，能够在空中进行有限度的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">喷气背包再充能</span>。<br><br>安装在喷气背包排气管周围的高效率压缩器利用了<span class=\"name name-stellar\">持续坠落</span>过程中产生的风流，将这些能量中的一部分回收到了喷气背包的燃料中。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">強化套裝噴射背包</span>的強大升級項目，能在空中提供有限的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">噴射背包補充能量</span>。<br><br>噴射背包排氣管周圍的高效能壓縮器能善用<span class=\"name name-stellar\">持續下降</span>的風流，回收該能量來補充噴射背包。"
  },
